body.description: The D-Link AX3200 Mesh Wi-Fi 6 Router (DIR-X3260) brings all the next-generation speed, capacity and range you need to handle today’s smart home. The DIR-X3260 offers Wi-Fi 6 speeds up to 800 Mbps (2.4 GHz) + 2402 Mbps (5 GHz), utilizing advanced features such as 1024-QAM, 8 simultaneous streams, OFDMA and MU-MIMO to enhance 4K streaming, online gaming and more. If you need more coverage down the road, D-Link’s Wi-Fi Mesh technology lets you add compatible D-Link Wi-Fi Mesh-enabled extenders or routers for more coverage. 4 Gigabit ports give you faster wired connectivity. Setup and enhanced parental controls are made easy with the free D-Link Wi-Fi app.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Next Generation WiFi Performance!! The D-Link AX3200 Mesh Wi-Fi 6 Router (DIR-X3260) brings all the next-generation speed, capacity and range you need to handle today’s smart home. The DIR-X3260 offers Wi-Fi 6 speeds up to 800 Mbps (2.4 GHz) + 2402 Mbps (5 GHz), utilizing advanced features such as 1024-QAM, 8 simultaneous streams, 4X4 antenna configuration, OFDMA and MU-MIMO to enhance 4K streaming, online gaming and more. Voice Control with the Google Assistant or Alexa lets you manage your network without lifting a finger. If you need more coverage down the road, D-Link’s Wi-Fi Mesh technology lets you add compatible D-Link Wi-Fi Mesh-enabled routers or extenders for more coverage. 4 Gigabit ports give you faster wired connectivity. Setup and enhanced parental controls are made easy with the free D-Link Wi-Fi app.

Next Gen WiFi 6 Up to 39% faster at 5GHz than the equivalent 11ac, the DIR-X3260 can handle everything the smart home can consume – 4K streaming, gaming, huge file downloads, edge devices like cameras and doorbells MU-MIMO Technology Great for multi-tasking households that same time video-chat, game, stream 4K More Efficient Data Transmission with OFDMA Today’s smart or connected homes are filled with devices hungry for WiFi bandwidth. Much like fully packed trucks transports goods, OFDMA works to move device data traffic simultaneously for more efficient transmission.

Extended Coverage Signals reach further throughout your home. Enhanced Parental Control Parental control to support profile based WiFi access Smart Home Works with the Google Assistant and Alexa. D-Link WiFi App Set up and manage your wireless network from your smartphone or tablet.

reviews.reviewText: Picked up my new d-link dir-x3260 today.Setup was a breeze and it works flawlessly.Amazon had it at a great price and easy pick up at Amazon hub locker . 5 stars for product and Amazon Canada.
I use this with a D-Link extender and have blazing speeds thru the house and on the deck.
This for WiFi so I don't to paid rent on the modem that I was using

I was excited to receive this and purchased as my previous wireless router was getting old. It was supposed to be a seamless process of plugging in and setting it up using an app. Unfortunately, although it showed signal, the wifi would not work at all in any devices. After 3 hours on the phone with DLink and him attempting multiple things, the router still would not provide an internet signal. It was first blamed that maybe it was my devices (MacBook and IPhones). After another few resets repeating the exact same process, the tech support then determined it was actually my internet modem (although, old router worked just fine with current modem) and that I would have to reach out to my internet company to get it working. I contacted my internet company who advised my internet modem was fine, performed a few additional tests and said that this is a faulty product.I would say the tech support for DLink was not at all helpful, but instead made me to feel as though I was dumb because their product wouldn’t work and was finding ways to blame all the products within the home.Just writing an honest review for those in the future looking to purchase a budget friendly wireless router.
Easy to setup and great signal!
